  "text": "As an ending question I will just ask is it possible, then, for the ipsissimus to have either positive or negative polarity, or must he be neither? I am Ra. We shall respond to the meaning of this term in a specialized sense. The ipsissimus is one who has mastered the Tree of Life and has used this mastery for negative polarization. Is there any brief query which we may respond to as we take leave of this instrument?",
